{"id":293092,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/global-voices-中国地震捐款保护咒/","date":"2013-05-11T18:00:11Z","modified":"2013-05-11T18:00:11Z","title":"Global Voices | 中国地震捐款保护咒","content":"<p><p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=524995667537476&#038;set=a.321611837875861.67317.200954406608272&#038;type=1&#038;theater\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/go-to-hell-150x300.jpg\" /></a>香港独立媒体网的Facebook专页，分享了中国社群媒体上广为流传的<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/inmediahk\">一张照片</a>，钞票上面被写了“咒语”，上头写着：“这是我捐给雅安的钱，哪个狗日敢贪死全家！”<br /><b></b><br />上周香港立法会基于多数香港民众压倒性的反对，<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2013/04/25/hong-kong-boycotts-donations-for-sichuan-earthquake/\">否决了捐款给中国地震灾民的要求</a>。民众害怕金钱会断送给贪腐的中国政府官员，而非送到需要的人们手中。</p>\n<div>校对者：Ameli</div>\n<p><span><span>作者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/author/oiwan/\" title=\"文章导读 Oiwan Lam\">Oiwan Lam</a></span> · <span>译者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/author/rio/\" title=\"文章导读 Rio\">Rio</a></span></span>  · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2013/04/29/a-spell-on-the-earthquake-donation-money-in-china/\" title=\"阅读原文  en\">阅读原文  en</a></span> · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/2013/05/12/12450/#comments\" title=\"则留言\">则留言 (0) </a></span><br />分享: <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.hemidemi.com/user_bookmark/new?title=%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%9C%B0%E9%9C%87%E6%8D%90%E6%AC%BE%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E5%92%92&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2013%2F05%2F12%2F12450%2F&#038;description=&#038;via=sticker\" title=\"HEMiDEMi\"><span>HEMiDEMi</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://mys